- Cloud Monitoring: dashboards and alerting policies
- Cloud Trace: distributed tracing for latency breakdown
- Private Service Connect: private connectivity for isolation
- Health checks and end-to-end tests

## Code Example

```javascript
// Example instrumentation snippet for Cloud Logging
const {Logging} = require('@google-cloud/logging');
const logging = new Logging();
const log = logging.log('api-logs');
const metadata = {resource: {type: 'cloud_run_revision', labels: {service: 'my-api', revision: 'rev-1'}}, severity: 'INFO'};
const traceId = 'TRACE_ID';
const entry = log.entry(metadata, {message: 'request received', trace: `projects/PROJECT_ID/traces/${traceId}`});
log.write(entry);
```

